"isVppDeviceBasedLicensingEnabled":true,"releaseNotes":"Minor bug fixes and improvements","version":"4.54.0","wrapperType":"software","currency":"NOK","description":"Organise your team, club or group. Save time. Focus on what matters. The free app trusted by millions of coaches, club admins, parents and players worldwide. Spond is the app that makes sports happen.\n\nWhether you're running a sports club or organising activities with your friends, Spond keeps everyone in sync. Stop chasing RSVPs, outdated contact info or late payments.\n\nWhat you can do:\n\n• Schedule training, matches and events\n• Set up recurring events for the whole season at once\n• Sync everything with your personal calendar\n• See who's coming with automatic RSVP tracking\n• Collect membership fees and event payments securely\n• Send reminders and keep track of who has paid\n• Manage multiple teams with sub groups and set member roles\n• Import members from Excel or add via link, email or SMS\n• Export attendance lists and data to Excel\n• Set up your starting line-ups for matches\n• Keep track of match goals and vote player of the match\n• Communicate via group chats, posts and polls\n• Store photos and documents in custom folders and file structures\n• Create fundraisers for your team to raise money\n• Manage children's accounts safely as a guardian with full visibility of communication with coaches\n\nBuilt for coaches, club admins, parents and players. Spond saves a coach on average 2 hours per week on admin tasks. That's more time on the pitch, less time in spreadsheets and group message chats.\n\nWorks for all sports and activities. Any group that needs to get organised will find their home in Spond.\n\nDownload Spond and make sports happen.","averageUserRating":4.67239,"trackCensoredName":"Spond","trackViewUrl":"https://apps.apple.com/no/app/spond/id755596884?uo=4","contentAdvisoryRating":"4+","averageUserRatingForCurrentVersion":4.67239,"languageCodesISO2A":["BG","HR","CS","DA","NL","